summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2011 TOYOTA SIENNA. THE CONTACT STATED THAT BOTH SLIDING DOORS ON THE VEHICLE FAILED TO OPEN AND CLOSE REMOTELY. ALSO, BOTH DOORS HAD TO BE CLOSED MANUALLY AND MADE AN ABNORMAL NOISE, AS IF THEY WERE STUCK. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO THE DEALER (LONGO TOYOTA, LOCATED ON 3534 PECK RD, EL MONTE, CA 91731), BUT WAS NOT REPAIRED DUE TO PART UNAVAILABILITY. THE DEALER INFORMED THE CONTACT TO WAIT FOR A SECOND RECALL NOTICE. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT REPAIRED. THE VIN WAS INCLUDED IN NHTSA CAMPAIGN NUMBER: 16V858000 (STRUCTURE). THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE. THE APPROXIMATE FAILURE MILEAGE 77,658. UPDATED 08/22/17*LJ   UPDATED 8/25/17*JS
